def semester(row):
    if row in [1,2,3]:
        return 1
    elif row in [4,5,6]:
        return 2
    elif row in [7,8,9]:
        return 3
    else:
        return 4
    
data['Semester'] = data['Month'].apply(lambda x: semester(x))
